name: Docker11
body:
`关于docker push出错：`

docekr　push docker/worker
错误信息如下：
2015/10/22 15:27:51 Error: Status 403 trying to push repository docker/worker: "Access Denied: 
Not allowed to create Repo at given location"      

最终gg到说仓库的名字必须是自己的名字开头．即＜your_register_name/your_image_name＞.

还有一种验证方式就是使用命令`docker login`进行验证．
